{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356980/extras/About_Game.jpg?t=1738768764\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fast paced and chaotic, EXON will require you to master the full array of death dealing tools at your disposal. Enemies possess a litany of spells and dark magic which will require precise gameplay in order to overcome the odds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356980/extras/gif_shotgun_hvga_320_30.gif?t=1738768764\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Formidable adversaries wielding unholy magic aim to overthrow your attempts to rid the realm of their unsanctified presence. Only the strongest of specimens will survive this twisted experiment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356980/extras/Gameplay.jpg?t=1738768764\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To ensure victory, you must master all elements of gameplay - weapons, abilities, augmentations and the environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356980/extras/gif_rifle_hvga_320_30.gif?t=1738768764\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Turn the balance in your favour with an assortment of augmentations that will bolster your\u00a0 arsenal and enhance your might on the battle field.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356980/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738768764","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356980/page.bg.jpg?t=1738768764","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/33569